{"tid":2508444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公社科新書反對「過洋節」 諷迪士尼麥當勞如穿軍服持槍「侵略」","createTime":"2021-04-28T18:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T19:31:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c17f594cec5a72140fe1c90208b0dd0090f153e9","tid":2508444,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"籲防西方軟實力在華滲透擴張<br />\n新學年中四級的公社科將由「『一國兩制』下的香港」部份開始教授，由名創教育出版的《新領域公民與社會發展》在「香港社會的多元文化特徵」課題中，提到全球化下西方文化漸成全球普遍接受的文化，中國不斷對外開放下，傳統習俗「正受到西方文化的衝擊，影響力不斷減少」。<br />\n<br />\n教師用書的補充資料更引用內地學者反對「過洋節」的文章，指非教徒「隨波逐流地認同基督教、耶誕節，無意中為基督教在中國的傳播與氾濫推波助瀾」，更使西方國家的軟實力在中國「不斷滲透和擴張」，呼籲「慎對耶誕節」，非教徒不要慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n該書續舉例指，聖誕節、萬聖節等西方節日受中國年輕一代歡迎，而重陽節、七夕等中國傳統節日受重視程度不斷下降。書中展示中國商場掛上聖誕裝飾的照片，問學生這反映中國可能面對甚麼「文化衝突」，參考答案指這反映西方節日受中國人重視，「可能對中國傳統節日造成衝擊，令這些節日被忽略甚至遺忘」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=bcb54019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&h=534d523e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/</a>"},{"pid":"2d91edcfab4568f6fa97d51676989a39c93da658","tid":2508444,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"仲以為係支那國內學校嘅圖書<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101fe31506b9dcab12341153829721ae6d279e8e","tid":2508444,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"#SENDTROOPSTOLIBERATEHK<br />\n#HKSOS<br />\n#LetMyPeopleGo<br />\n#HKEXITBAN<br />\n#GiveHKersArms<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n##CCP_is_terrorist<br />\n<br />\n[Twitter戰線] 煲大港共封港法案 狂推Hashtags求救<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2507940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2507940</a>"},{"pid":"83dad9056cd168c65ccdffde57360ddaca30aa68","tid":2508444,"uid":213397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:56:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚著衫啦 著返唐裝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757b02beee6c067f1c8f13f490915b961a702383","tid":2508444,"uid":76216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:58:11.000Z","msg":"西裝唔好叫西裝啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4aa0a1635880734d49ea9861d2264b5fca17e9","tid":2508444,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"馬克思列寧主義係乜方思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d508487f99da31f2d0dc1d762713af62e467103","tid":2508444,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:06:39.000Z","msg":"BTW<br />\n支持罷食老麥<br />\n罷睇罷去迪士尼"},{"pid":"ba042f0d7f1f7fab263d00efc376d291c415bed5","tid":2508444,"uid":40216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:06:49.000Z","msg":"支持驅逐金拱門出中國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0128c0839541f881ad08eee4144ba9732d38b92","tid":2508444,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"見到軟實力三個字已經唔撚駛睇<br />\n支共蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31f72472ca9a2f7c61f20b20b60fc45a1ed08af","tid":2508444,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-